divs: Sighting Detailsgoing to work k-9 sky was vibrating--coming up cypress creek rd when very low fireball went right in front of me and went toward executive airport --scared the crap out of me---i turned to old mcnabb rd sky still vibrating another one goes by much higher-pefect comets but the sky was starting to quit shaking--i called executive airport to ask them if they seen it --told me someone would call me later never heard a word from them--i will never forget that day almost shaking writing this--willing to take lie detector or whatever--i seen it plain as day it was going very slow seen it for about 3 min
Summary: comet very low flying 200ft at most then another higher
